cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NA, cs.AI 

The paper deals with image restoration and deconvolution, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of Bayesian models and algorithms also suggests a potential fit for machine learning (cs.MM) and numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories. Additionally, the application of the proposed methods to enhance the detection of disease signatures in OEM images could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
